      • SoftwareProfile

        public SoftwareProfile(java.lang.String profileName,
                       java.lang.String profilePassword,
                       java.lang.String defaultRegion,
                       java.lang.String defaultLanguage,
                       java.lang.String defaultRiotAccount,
                       java.lang.String riotAPIKey)
        The main constructor
        Parameters:
        profileName - A String for the SoftwareProfile's name (Required).
        profilePassword - A String for the SoftwareProfile's password, no encryption yet (Required).
        defaultRegion - Optional String for SoftwareProfile's default League of Legends region.
        defaultLanguage - Optional String for SoftwareProfile's default user interface language. Should follow the format of "language_country", e.g. "en_US" or "fi_FI".
        defaultRiotAccount - Optional String for an encrypted version of Riot's accountId. Not in use yet.
        riotAPIKey - Partially optional String for the SoftwareProfile's Riot API-key. Mandatory to get the program working as it should.
